dreisoft.tresos.tresosdb.api.model.v1.genericstructure.infrastructure.autosar

Interface IARPackage

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IEntity, IIdentifiable

    public interface IARPackage
extends IEntity, IIdentifiable
    IARPackage: Entity class of the tresosDB model.

    AUTOSAR package, allowing to create top level packages to structure the contained ARElements. ARPackages are open sets, which means that in a file based description system, multiple files can be used to partially describe the contents of a package. This is an extended version of MSR's SW-SYSTEM.
